Dummy Crack Instructions for Corel PaintShop Pro X3 by IRONHIDE:
Software needed for install: Winrar. Download at: www.rarlabs.com Use Winrar to extract the .rar archive. 
1. Extract Paintshop Pro X3 from "Corel PaintShop Photo Pro X3 v13.2.0.4 + KeyGen [TrT-TcT]" Rar archives.

2. IF DURING EXTRACTION, YOUR ANTIVIRUS PROGRAM POPS UP AND WARNS YOU ABOUT THE "KEYGEN", TELL IT TO IGNORE IT OR ADD TO EXCLUSIONS.

3. Go into the "Corel PaintShop Photo Pro X3 v13.2.0.4 [TrT-TcT]" Folder.

1. Turn off/Disable internet on your computer.
2. Install Paintshop by running "PSPP_X3_TBYB.exe".
3. Run Paintshop.
4. When 30 day trial window opens, choose "register later".
5. Allow Paintshop to open, then exit out of it.
6. Another registration window opens encouraging you to buy the Pro version.
6. On the bottom left choose the link that says something like: "already purchased enter serial".
7. Go into the â€œCorel.PSP.X3.Keymaker-COREâ€ folder and run â€œkeygen.exeâ€ and click "key code".
8. Copy the "key code" and paste it into Paintshop registration window "serial" section.
9. Click "phone corel" in the Paintshop registration window.
10. Copy the "Installation Code" from the Paintshop registration window and paste into keygen "installation code" secion.
11. Click "generate" in the keygen.
12. Copy the "activation code" from the keygen and paste into the Paintshop registration window "activation code" section.
13. Click "continue" in the Paintshop registration window.
14. Click "close" in the Paintshop registration window.
15. Done.

Happy Paintshop pro full version-ing!  ~ IRONHIDE  :-)
